## 📁 DIRECTORY STRUCTURE

```
apps/web/                  # Next.js 14 frontend
  ├── app/                 # App Router (pages + layouts)
  ├── components/          # React components
  ├── lib/                 # api.ts, sentry.ts, utils
  └── next.config.js

services/api/              # NestJS backend
  ├── src/modules/         # Modular structure (auth, kyc, obras, etc)
  ├── prisma/              # Migrations + schema
  └── nest-cli.json

packages/
  ├── @imbobi/schemas/     # Zod validation (source of truth)
  ├── @imbobi/core/        # Hooks, utils, api-client
  └── @imbobi/ui/          # Components (shadcn + React Native)
```

