## 📊 OBSERVABILITY REQUIREMENTS

### Structured Logging
```typescript
// ✅ DO THIS
this.logger.log('Obra created', {
  obraId: obra.id,
  usuarioId: usuario.id,
  endereco: obra.endereco,
  timestamp: new Date(),
});

// ❌ DON'T DO THIS
console.log('Created obra:', obra);
```

### Distributed Tracing
```typescript
// Add trace context to critical operations
const span = tracer.startSpan('processar_etapa', {
  attributes: { 'etapa.id': etapaId }
});

// Automatically traced:
// - validate()
// - processarDocumentos()
// - triggearAprovacao()

span.end();
```

### Metrics
```typescript
// Track business metrics
this.metrics.increment('obras_criadas_total', {
  status: obra.status,
  tipo: obra.tipo,
});

this.metrics.histogram('etapa_processamento_ms', processingTime);
```

