## 🔐 SECURITY RULES

### 1. Authorization
```typescript
// ✅ Always check authorization
if (obra.usuarioId !== currentUser.id && !currentUser.isAdmin) {
  throw new ForbiddenException();
}

// ❌ Never assume user has access
return obra;  // Without checking!
```

### 2. Input Validation
```typescript
// ✅ Always validate with Zod
const obra = obraSchema.parse(req.body);

// ❌ Never trust client input
const obra = req.body;
```

### 3. Secrets
```bash
# ✅ Use environment variables
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...

# ❌ Never commit secrets
password = "secret123"
```

### 4. Audit Logging
```typescript
// Log sensitive operations
this.auditService.log({
  action: 'APPROVE_KYC',
  entityId: kycId,
  userId: managerId,
  changes: { before: oldStatus, after: 'APROVADO' },
  timestamp: new Date(),
});
```

