## 🎯 COMMON MISTAKES TO AVOID

| ❌ Mistake | ✅ Correct |
|-----------|----------|
| Using `any` type | Specific types or `unknown` |
| No error handling | Try/catch + logging |
| Hardcoded URLs | Environment variables |
| Sync heavy operations | Use BullMQ queues |
| No timeout on calls | Always set timeout |
| Duplicating validation | Use Zod schemas |
| Modifying audit logs | Immutable event sourcing |
| No caching | 3-tier cache strategy |
| No circuit breaker | Implement for external APIs |
| Silent failures | Always log + alert |

